<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Transaction Accepted</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Urbanist:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Urbanist", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .top-bar {
        height: 6px;
        background-color: #004de8;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .logo {
        height: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #004de8;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 16px 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .status-message {
        background-color: #e2f7e2;
        color: #28a745;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #004de8;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        padding: 14px 24px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      a {
        color: #004de8;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #004de8;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .transaction-details {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 24px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .transaction-details p {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="top-bar"></div>
      <div class="content">
        <img
          src="https://yourdomain.com/logo.png"
          alt="Eventure Logo"
          class="logo"
        />
        <h1>Transaction Accepted</h1>

        <p>Hi <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>
          We are happy to inform you that your recent transaction for
          <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> has been accepted by the organizer.
        </p>

        <div class="status-message">
          ✅ Your transaction has been successfully accepted.
        </div>

        <p>Here are the details of your transaction:</p>

        <div class="transaction-details">
          <div class="feature-list">
            <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transactionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Event Name:</strong> {{eventName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Date and Time:</strong> {{transactionDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{transactionAmount}}</p>
            <p>
              <strong>Status:</strong>
              <span style="color: #28a745; font-weight: 600">Accepted</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>
          We look forward to seeing you at the event. If you need any further
          information or assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to the
          organizer directly.
        </p>

        <a href="{{eventLink}}" class="button">Go to Event Page</a>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:eventureoffic@gmail.com">eventureoffic@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for using Eventure!</p>
        <p>— The Eventure Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        © 2025 Eventure. All rights reserved.<br />
        <a href="https://eventure.com">Visit our website</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
